{% extends "_includes/default.njk" %}

{% block title %}Opt-Out Machine by Known Privacy{% endblock %}
{% set description = "The motivation for creating the Opt-Out Machine was to take a step toward getting our privacy back." %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="bg-neutral flex relative bg-cover bg-no-repeat h-[640px] blog-post-hero">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-6xl leading-none capitalize text-white mt-96 p-24">Motivation</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-neutral flex flex-row">
    <div class="px-56">
      <h1 class="font-semibold text-3xl leading-relaxed capitalize mt-12 mb-2">We created the Opt-Out Machine <br>because we want our privacy back.</h1>
      <p class="my-8 text-lg">And as anyone watching can see, surveillance is getting more commonplace. If we don't act to get our privacy back, we can expect:</p>
      <ul class="ml-4 leading-loose">
        <li class="list-none hover:list-disc pl-2 mt-3 text-lg">More stolen credit card numbers</li>
        <li class="list-none hover:list-disc pl-2 mt-3 text-lg">Higher possibility of identity theft</li>
        <li class="list-none hover:list-disc pl-2 mt-3 text-lg">Greater feeling that we need to self-censor on the Internet</li>
        <li class="list-none hover:list-disc pl-2 mt-3 text-lg">More egregious data leaks by corporations affecting you</li>
        <li class="list-none hover:list-disc pl-2 mt-3 text-lg">More government overreach</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="bg-neutral flex flex-row mt-16 px-56">
      <h1 class="font-semibold text-3xl capitalize">Our Responsibilities</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-neutral flex flex-row my-10 px-56">
    <div class="basis-2/3">
      <p class="text-lg">As the makers of the Opt-Out Machine, our commitments to you are:</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside ml-4 leading-loose">
        <li class="mt-3 text-lg">To be good stewards of your personal information, only holding the minimum needed to make privacy requests</li>
        <li class="mt-3 text-lg">To maintain a focus on your security in the design and maintenance of our systems</li>
        <li class="mt-3 text-lg">To tell you the truth in a timely manner and remedy the situation to the best of our ability if we screw up</li>
        <li class="mt-3 text-lg">A corporate charter that says even if our company merges with another company, your data can never be sold or used in a way that you have not explicitly agreed to</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="basis-1/3">
      <img class="float-right" src="{{ '/images/public-benefit-corporation.svg' | url }}" alt="public benefit corporation">
    </div>
  </div>
{% endblock %}
